<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">August 3, 2001 | Page 15</font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">OTHER STORIES BELOW<br>
<a href="#Times"><i>New York Times</i></a><br>
<a href="#WBAI">WBAI</a><br>
<a href="#Supremo">V&amp;V Supremo Foods</a><br>
